cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.HC 

The paper proposes a deep learning approach for facial action unit detection, which involves enhancing and cropping regions of interest. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The approach also involves attention maps and convolutional layers, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. Finally, the application of the approach is in human-computer interaction (cs.HC), as it aims to improve the detection of facial expressions.
